unnamat-girīndra-	the mountain having come up
nyasta-eka-sthiratara-hasta-paṅkajam	placed one strong lotus hand firmly
tvām	Thou
abhrānte	in the heavens
vidhi-giriśa-ādaya:	Brahmaa Shiva and other gods
pramodāt-udbhrāntā	overwhelmed with joy
